title: The REAL Reason Batgirl was Canceled #shorts

media:group.media:title: The REAL Reason Batgirl was Canceled #shorts
media:group.media:description:
Despite nearly being finished and amassing $90 million in production costs, Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD) decided to cancel Batgirl. Why in the world would anyone make that decision after investing so much into it? Watch this FEE #short to find out.
